At AM PM, we're experts in creating premium bathroom products that redefine the essence of luxury living. As we push ahead, shattering barriers and achieving new milestones, we're seeking outstanding professionals in Procurement to join our team!





 Tasks



* Organization and control of the company’s procurement processes;

* Development and implementation of the procurement strategy;

* Cost optimization and procurement budget management;

* Monitoring compliance with delivery deadlines and quality standards;

* Management of turnover and stock levels;

* Inventory analysis and demand forecasting;

* Interaction with logistics, production, and finance departments;

* Leadership of the procurement team, training and development of employees;

* Preparation of reports and analytics on procurement activities;

* Selection, evaluation, and development of suppliers, negotiation management.





 Requirements



* Higher education;

* At least 3 years of experience in a managerial position;

* Proficiency in
 **English and Russian** 
 (both written and spoken)

* Analytical mindset, leadership skills, strategic thinking;

* Strong organizational and systematic approach.





 Benefits



* Access to a comfortable workspace situated in Dubai.

* Full\-time employment schedule (5 days a week)

* Active team

* Career growth, interesting tasks

* Rich corporate culture






 Important: The HR department accepts responses only through the JOIN platform, please send us a resume in this way, other communication methods are not available

